            In this blog we'll take a look at our "settings". This page's
            purpose solely lies in giving our users the possibility to create
            games with their preferred settings.
            <br />
            In our settings-menu the user can change the gamemode, total rounds
            played, player capacity of the lobby and the maximum allowed time
            for guessing the answers to our questions. We plan to implement
            these options as drop-down-menus. Additionally, the user can also
            choose to create the lobby as a public lobby or to be only
            accessible with a code (private game). All options will be filled
            with default values at the beginning.
            <br />
