            <br />
            On the picture below you can see the mockup from a player's view.
            It's simple and straight forward while showing all the details you
            need to know. In the center we plan to show our Logo and the
            gamecode below, so you can always tell your friends in which lobby
            they need to join to be able to guess with you. A list of all
            players, led by the lobby's creator is shown beneath. The left-hand
            side shows all the important information about your chosen settings.
            Additionally, a short description of your gamemode is available on
            the right-hand side. While "normal" players can only see one button
